Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy explains how LEDit ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and handles information when you use our app. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to handling any data responsibly.
1. Data Collection
We do not collect any personal data. However, we gather anonymous analytics data regarding the device (such as model and system version) and usage data to improve user experience and for marketing purposes.
2. Data Use
The collected anonymous data is used solely for the following purposes:
Enhancing the app's functionality and user experience.
Understanding app usage trends for marketing and improvement.
3. Third-Party Services
We use trusted third-party services to assist in the collection and analysis of anonymous data:
TelemetryDeck (used for analytics)
RevenueCat (used for managing subscriptions and purchases)
These third-party services have their own privacy policies that govern their handling of data.
4. Data Sharing
We do not share your data with any other third parties outside of the services mentioned above. Data collected remains anonymous and is used solely for internal purposes.
5. Device Permissions
Our app does not require access to any device permissions such as the camera, microphone, or contacts.
6. Security
We prioritize the security of the data collected by employing appropriate measures, including authentication processes, to safeguard it.
7. User Data Control
Since we do not collect personal data, there is no data available for users to update, access, or delete.
8. Compliance
We comply with all applicable data protection laws and regulations within the EU.
9. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify users of any significant changes.
10. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us
here
